72、 Frank O’connor奧康納1903-1966 論文集：The Lonely Voice:A Study of the Short Story寂寞之聲：短篇小說研究自傳：An Only Son獨生子;My Father’s Son;The Backward Look:A Survey of Irish Literature愛爾蘭文學回顧短篇小說集：Collection Two:Stories by Frank O’connor(Private Property私有財產)
73、Evelyn Waugh伊夫林·沃1903-1966 長篇小說：Decline and Fall沒落與墮落;Vile Bodies行屍走肉;A Handful of Dust 一撮灰塵;Black Mischief黑色的禍害;Scoop挖新聞;Put out More Flags多升幾面旗;Bridgeshead Revisited重遊布賴茲海德(Men at Arms行伍生涯;Officers and Gentlemen軍官與紳士;Unconditional Surrender無條件投降→The Sword of Honour榮譽之劍三部曲)自傳：A Little Learning一點學問（三部只成一部）短篇小說集：Mr Loveday’s Little Outing and Other Sad Stories洛弗戴先生一次短暫的外出與其他悲慘故事
74、Christopher Isherwood 衣修午德1904- All the Conspirators所有的陰謀者;Mr Norris Changeds Traits諾裏斯先生換火車;Sally Bowles薩利·鮑爾斯（選自《再見吧，柏林》）;Journey to a War戰地行;Prater Violet紫羅蘭姑娘;The World in the Evening夜晚的世界;Down there on A Visit在那兒進行訪問;A Single Man單身漢;A Meeting by the River河畔相會
75、Graham Greene格雷厄姆·格林1904- 消遣：Stamboul Train斯坦布爾列車;A Gun for Sale一支出賣的槍;Our Man in Havana我們在哈瓦納的人嚴肅：The Power and the Glory權力與榮譽;The Heart of the Matter問題的核心;The End of the Affair愛情的結局;The Quiet American;The Comedians喜劇演員;The Human Favor人的因素 
76、Charles Percy Snow斯諾1905-1980 Strangers and Brothers陌生人與兄弟們;The Light and the Dark光明與黑暗;Time of Hope希望的時刻;The Masters院長們;The New Men新人;Homecoings歸家;The Conscience of the Rich富人的良心;The Affairs事件;Corridors of Power權力走廊;The Sleep of Reason理智沉眠;Last Things結局
77、 Peter Courtney Quennell昆納爾1905- Byron:The Year of Fame拜倫：盛名時期;Byron in Italy;Byron:A Self-Portrait拜倫：一幅自我畫像;A History of English Literature;Four Portraits:Studies of the 18th Century四幅畫像：關於十八世紀的研究
78、 William Empson燕卜蓀1906- 詩集：Poems;The Gathering Storm醞釀中的風暴;Collected Poems名詩：Legal Fiction;Homage to the British Museum論著：Seven Types of Ambiguity晦澀的七種類型;Some Versions of Pastoral田園詩的幾種變化；The Structure of Complex Words複合詞的結構
79、Wystan Hugh Auden奧登1907-1973 詩集：Poems;The Orators雄辯家;Look,Stranger!瞧，陌生人;Spain詩劇：The Dog Beneath the Skin皮下之狗;The Ascent,F6攀登F6;On the Frontier邊界上The Sea and the Mirror海與鏡;The Age of Anxiety憂慮時代;The Shield of Achilles阿基琉斯的盾牌;Homage to Clio向克奧女神致敬;About the House屋子內外散文評論集：The Dyer’s Hand染工之手;Secondary World次要的世界名詩：Who’s Who;The Unknown Citizen;Their Lonely Betters
80、William Golding戈爾丁1911- 長篇小說：Lord of the Flies蠅王;The Inheritors繼承人;Pincher Martin平卻·馬丁;The Spire塔尖;The Pyramid金字塔
81、 Angus Wilson威爾遜1913- 小說：The Wrong Set and Other Storie亂了套和其他短篇故事s;Anglo-Saxon Attitudes盎格魯撒克遜態度;The Middle Age of Mrs Eliot艾略特夫人的中年;The Old Men at the Zoo; Late Call夜訪;As if by Magic像是用了魔術評論：Emile Zole愛彌爾·佐拉;The World of Charles Dickens;The Strange Ride of Rudyard Kipling吉卜林的奇異旅程
82、Dylon Thomas迪倫·托馬斯1914-1953 詩：Eighteen Poems;The Map of Love愛的地圖;Deaths and Entrances死亡與出場;Collected Poems自傳：Portrait of the Artist as a Young Dog作為一條小狗的藝術家畫像廣播劇：Under the Milk Wood 名詩：Do Not Go Gentle Into That Good Night
83、Muriel Sarah Spark斯帕克1918- The Comforter安慰者;The Prime of Miss Jean Brodie瓊·布羅迪小姐的黃金時代;The Diver’s Seat司機的座位;The Abbess of Crewe克魯女修道院院長;Loitering with Intent存心遊戲;Collected Stories I短篇小說集（一）
84、 Richard Lessing多麗絲·萊辛1919- The Grass is Singing草兒在歌唱;Children of Violence暴力和孩子們(Martha Quest瑪莎·金奎特 ;A Proper Marriage正當的婚姻;A Ripple from the Storm暴風雨掀起的漣漪;Landlocked被陸地圍住的;The Four-gated City四門城);The Golden Notebook金色筆記;Briefing for a Descent into Hell墮入地獄簡況;The Summer before the Dark
85、Iris Murdoch默多克1919- Under the Net在網下;The Bel鐘l;A Severed Head砍掉的頭;The Black Prince黑衣王子;The Sea,The Sea大海啊，大海
86、 Philip Larkin拉金1922- 詩：The North Ship北方船;Jill;A Girl in Winter詩集：The Less Deceived受騙較少的人;The Whitsun Weddings降靈節婚禮;High Windows高窗名詩：Church Going;Reason for Attendance
87、Kingsley Amis 金斯萊·艾米斯1922- 小說：Lucky Jim幸運的吉姆;My Enemy’s Enemy我的敵人的敵人;One Fat Englishman一個英國胖子;That Uncertain Feeling那種不安感;Take a Girl Like You愛你這樣的姑娘;Ending up死
88、 John Wain韋恩1925- 長篇小說：Hurry on Down大學後的漂泊;Living in the Present生活在當代;The Contenders競爭者;Strike the Father Dead打死父親;A Winter in the Hills山中寒冬短篇小說集：The Life Guard救生員
89、Brian Wilson Aldiss奧爾迪斯1925- The Brightfountain Diaries明泉日記; The Billion Year Spree:The History of Science Fiction科幻小說史;Best SF Stories of Brian W Aldiss奧爾迪斯最佳科幻故事集(Outside外界)
90、Alan Sillitoe西利托1928- Saturday Night and Sunday Morning;The General;Key to the Door;A Tree on Fire;A Start in Life一位長跑運動員的孤獨;The Loneliness of the Long-Distance Runner撿破爛人的女兒;The Ragman’s Daughter;The Windower’s Son
91、 John Osborne奧斯本1929- Look back in Anger憤怒的回顧;Lurther;Inadmissible Evidence不能接受的證據;Time Present and Hotel in Amsterdam目前和阿姆斯特丹的旅館
92、 Ted Hughs特德·休斯1930- The Hawk in the Rain雨中鷹;Lupercal盧潑卡爾神(Hawk of Roosting);Scapegoats and Rabies替罪羊與狂犬病;Wodwo沃德沃怪物;Crow烏鴉Songs of Woe哀歌
93、 Arnold Wesker韋斯克1932- 劇本：The Wesker Triology韋斯克三部曲(Chicken Soup with Barley大麥雞湯;Roots;I’m Talking about Jerusalem0;The Four Seasons;The Friends;The Journalists新聞記者;Caritas Christi卡裏塔斯·克裏斯蒂
